about.description: Read PDS and Isis Cube files as NumPy arrays
about.summary: Python PDS and Isis Cube file parser.

name: planetaryimage
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "planetaryimage" %}
{% set version = "0.5.0" %}
{% set sha256 = "6b6af0d83147fe3fc4550ea753557010f01dd1bf905e060f7b942b3f16b38def" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 1
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - numpy
    - pvl
    - six

test:
  imports:
    - planetaryimage

about:
  home: http://github.com/planetarypy/planetaryimage
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Python PDS and Isis Cube file parser.'

  description: |
    Read PDS and Isis Cube files as NumPy arrays
  doc_url: https://planetaryimage.readthedocs.org/
  dev_url: https://github.com/planetarypy/planetaryimage

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - pbvarga1
